# runapp and restartall commands

When the user says **runapp**, **runall**, or **restartall**, do the following. **runall** is an alias for **runapp**. The same rebuild-and-refresh procedure (run runapp script, then browser_tabs, then browser_navigate to refresh) is **mandatory after every feature and bug fix** — see the rule "post-feature-rebuild-and-refresh".

## Canonical port

**The app always runs on `http://localhost:3000`.** After runapp or restartall, always navigate the Cursor Browser to `http://localhost:3000?_=<timestamp>`, never 3001 or any other port.

## runapp

**Goal:** Kill all existing dev servers, build the app fresh, start a new dev server on port 3000, and refresh the existing Cursor Browser tab to `http://localhost:3000`.

**runapp ALWAYS kills and restarts the dev server.** This is required because reusing an existing dev server after a new build causes asset hash mismatches — the HTML references new `?v=` timestamps but the old server doesn't serve them, causing CSS/JS 404s and a broken app.

The script:
1. Kills any existing Next.js dev servers on ports 3000, 3001, 3002, 3003.
2. Waits briefly for ports to be fully released.
3. Runs `npm run build`.
4. Starts a fresh `npm run dev` server on port 3000.

**Do not reuse or navigate to port 3001, 3002, or 3003.**

1. Run `npm run runapp` or `npm run runall`.
2. Wait 4–6 s for the new dev server to be ready (it always starts fresh).
3. **Always refresh to port 3000:** Call `browser_tabs` with `action: "list"`. Call `browser_navigate` with `http://localhost:3000?_=<timestamp>`. This ensures the browser loads from the canonical port with the latest build.

## restartall

Same behavior as runapp — use either command interchangeably.

1. Run `npm run restartall` (kills all dev servers on 3000/3001/3002/3003, rebuilds, starts fresh on 3000).
2. Wait 4–6 s for the server to be ready.
3. Navigate the existing Cursor Browser tab to `http://localhost:3000?_=<timestamp>`.

## Summary

| Command     | Script does                          | Agent then                    |
|------------|---------------------------------------|-------------------------------|
| **runapp** / **runall** | Kill all dev servers on 300x, build, start fresh on 3000 | Wait 4-6s, navigate browser to `http://localhost:3000?_=<ts>` |
| **restartall** | Kill all dev servers on 300x, build, start fresh on 3000 | Wait 4-6s, navigate browser to `http://localhost:3000?_=<ts>` |
